message.body: I'm at Nakul's. Lauren, I think I'm starting to care about him. Hellppppp. I don't like it I don't like it I don't like it.
Wait, what are you doing? I need to come home and take my medicine. He's going to be the death of me.
i'm in lullwater taking pictures. i also realized some things about andrew. ugh. also are you planning on being home tonight after trivia?
We need to talkkkk. I'm freaking out and I want to hear your realizations. And idk. Nakul wants to take me to dinner and we're supposed to study, but I don't kn
ow when. I can probably avoid the room pretty easily.

hopefully i'll be back in time to shower and clean and we can talk then, but the quizbowl team wants to party (aka answer questions whilst intoxicated) and i volunteered our room. you're more than welcome to be there, you're actually invited, but if you were planning on schoolwork or something i didn't want to bother you.
Oh fuck. I have to clean. I was in a panic last night and dumped all my laundry on my bed. As you witnessed. And that sounds like a lot of fun. I might join you
depending on how much work I get done.
yay! so if you've got dinner plans then i'm guessing you're not coming to trivia?
I don't know. I'm waiting for Nakul to get the fuck out of the shower. I swear he's a girl.
I think I'm ###########, hahahaha. I've never experienced this kind of intense lust before and it's awfulllll.
hahahahahahahahahahaha. my favorite thing you've ever said.
Had a panic attack because I thought that I lost my keys. Turns out they were wedged between my boobs and my computer. Hate my life.
